      • getName

        public String getName()
        Description copied from interface: GremlinPlugin
        The name of the plugin. This name should be unique (use a namespaced approach) as naming clashes will prevent proper plugin operations. Plugins developed by TinkerPop will be prefixed with "tinkerpop." For example, TinkerPop's implementation of Giraph would be named "tinkerpop.giraph". If Facebook were to do their own implementation the implementation might be called "facebook.giraph".
